package system.services.phm


// Platform Health Management — the {Gate; Fsm} split (same idiom as SM): PhmGate
// is the wire-reachable ingest (subscribes to the supervisor + node + app health
// signals, does the threshold counting) and PhmFsm is the per-entity fault state
// machine it post_event()s into in-process. Both prototypes share one process.
// PhmTester is probe-only (in no composition).
composition Phm {
    prototype PhmFsm  phm_fsm
    prototype PhmGate phm_gate
}
